# HSM collector conformance v1 — rate sensor contract.
# Format: case|action|arg1|arg2|...
# Actions:
# create_rate_sensor|path|post_period_ms
# add_rate|idx|value|status|comment           (invalid value/status increments are silently dropped)
# add_rate_raw|idx|value|raw_status|comment   (raw numeric status — used for invalid-status cases)
# expect_eventually_payload_contains|substring|timeout_s
# expect_eventually_value_above|threshold|timeout_s
# Contract notes:
# - Rate = accumulated sum / measured elapsed seconds since the previous post; the sum resets on
#   every post. The exact value is timing-dependent, so portable cases assert invariants only
#   (zeros when idle, eventually-positive after adds); the elapsed-time math itself is pinned by
#   language-local unit tests.
# - The FIRST post fires immediately on Start (schedule due time = 0), then every post period.
# - Status and comment are sticky: the last accepted increment's status/comment ride on every
#   subsequent post until changed.
# - Stop does NOT flush the pending sum (deliberate: a partial-window rate is alert-noise risk;
#   data preservation at stop applies to bars, not rates). The accumulated sum survives a
#   stop -> start cycle and rides the immediate first post of the next run, divided by the
#   CONFIGURED period (the restart resets the elapsed baseline, not the accumulator — mirrors
#   C# MonitoringRateSensor.InitAsync).

rate_posts_zero_when_idle|create_collector
rate_posts_zero_when_idle|create_rate_sensor|contract/rate/idle|100
rate_posts_zero_when_idle|start
rate_posts_zero_when_idle|expect_sent_count_between|2|1000|10
rate_posts_zero_when_idle|expect_all_payloads_contain|"Type":9,
rate_posts_zero_when_idle|expect_all_payloads_contain|"Value":0,
rate_posts_zero_when_idle|expect_all_payloads_contain|"Status":1,

rate_posts_positive_value_after_adds|create_collector
rate_posts_positive_value_after_adds|create_rate_sensor|contract/rate/adds|150
rate_posts_positive_value_after_adds|start
rate_posts_positive_value_after_adds|add_rate|0|60|Ok|adds
rate_posts_positive_value_after_adds|add_rate|0|40|Ok|adds
rate_posts_positive_value_after_adds|expect_eventually_value_above|0|10

rate_status_and_comment_are_sticky|create_collector
rate_status_and_comment_are_sticky|create_rate_sensor|contract/rate/sticky|100
rate_status_and_comment_are_sticky|start
rate_status_and_comment_are_sticky|add_rate|0|5|Warning|sticky-comment
rate_status_and_comment_are_sticky|expect_eventually_payload_contains|"Status":2,|10
rate_status_and_comment_are_sticky|expect_eventually_payload_contains|sticky-comment|10

rate_invalid_status_increment_is_dropped|create_collector
rate_invalid_status_increment_is_dropped|create_rate_sensor|contract/rate/bad-status|100
rate_invalid_status_increment_is_dropped|start
rate_invalid_status_increment_is_dropped|add_rate_raw|0|100|99|bad-status
rate_invalid_status_increment_is_dropped|expect_sent_count_between|2|1000|10
rate_invalid_status_increment_is_dropped|expect_all_payloads_contain|"Value":0,
rate_invalid_status_increment_is_dropped|expect_all_payloads_contain|"Status":1,

rate_nan_increment_is_dropped|create_collector
rate_nan_increment_is_dropped|create_rate_sensor|contract/rate/nan|100
rate_nan_increment_is_dropped|start
rate_nan_increment_is_dropped|add_rate|0|NaN|Ok|nan-increment
rate_nan_increment_is_dropped|expect_sent_count_between|2|1000|10
rate_nan_increment_is_dropped|expect_all_payloads_contain|"Value":0,

rate_stop_drops_pending_sum|create_collector
rate_stop_drops_pending_sum|create_rate_sensor|contract/rate/stop|60000
rate_stop_drops_pending_sum|start
rate_stop_drops_pending_sum|expect_sent_count|1|5
rate_stop_drops_pending_sum|add_rate|0|100|Ok|pending
rate_stop_drops_pending_sum|stop
rate_stop_drops_pending_sum|expect_sent_count|1
rate_stop_drops_pending_sum|expect_all_payloads_contain|"Value":0,

rate_restart_carries_pending_sum_over_configured_period|create_collector
rate_restart_carries_pending_sum_over_configured_period|create_rate_sensor|contract/rate/restart|60000
rate_restart_carries_pending_sum_over_configured_period|start
rate_restart_carries_pending_sum_over_configured_period|expect_sent_count|1|5
rate_restart_carries_pending_sum_over_configured_period|add_rate|0|100|Ok|carried
rate_restart_carries_pending_sum_over_configured_period|stop
rate_restart_carries_pending_sum_over_configured_period|expect_sent_count|1
rate_restart_carries_pending_sum_over_configured_period|start
rate_restart_carries_pending_sum_over_configured_period|expect_sent_count|2|5
rate_restart_carries_pending_sum_over_configured_period|expect_eventually_value_above|1|5
